{"tid":51861,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"條女比好人卡你但又留假希望比你","createTime":"2016-12-23T14:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T00:06:30.000Z","uid":68734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"635f9b4013d1fad16be305cde56dda3ac5c7ad4f","tid":51861,"uid":68734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:30:54.000Z","msg":"上個星期同暗戀既女仔表左白<br />\n結果可能太急 / 自己太毒比人派好人卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但條女當時係話自己覺得感情係要日月累積，而且又自己提起下個星期單獨約食飯既事（之前約過佢佢未覆）<br />\n<br />\n我當時覺得仲有希望，想繼續同佢慢慢發展<br />\n<br />\n結果個日之後佢whatsapp就明顯冷淡左...<br />\n到左今日本身講好左食飯，佢又好明顯扮病咁放左我飛機.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我忍唔住求左佢，可唔可以講d野令我死心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解你已經決定左做到咁絕，當時又要比假希望我"},{"pid":"cd6b7661faef97c598d8717a790f9f49e4cb496e","tid":51861,"uid":68734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e407e5a836c0bd9f087d262dca273f8c5d88f3b","tid":51861,"uid":64464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"你諗太多啦"},{"pid":"a8eeeeca3354e104fc7037cad24b86feb2336e7a","tid":51861,"uid":301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"D女個腦裝屎"},{"pid":"91e1d874db278397a55eb115cc5bbb463221cd95","tid":51861,"uid":68734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你諗太多啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我上個星期已經諗太多...<br />\n不過點都好，如今已經無希望<br />\n<br />\n佢亦都無再覆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f436190186551f599a76c777194cb59f4fcf65b","tid":51861,"uid":68734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:02:16.000Z","msg":"如今只求一句令我死心既說話<br />\n點解你咁樣都唔可以比我<br />\n<br />\n我係咪低賤到連比人拒絕既機會都唔值得"},{"pid":"4a97e7f175ca7e60f0f4a1c3b4d5b82c6b425e04","tid":51861,"uid":2191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:26:58.000Z","msg":"我以為個post係我開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4e86962683720b92cac54c30935a17ff88773c","tid":51861,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"我唔係一個好女仔"},{"pid":"d58e2ef08aa9eedb13649bb540fa12f5ccc4a74d","tid":51861,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"留一線，想收你做兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好令佢日後仲可以利用你"},{"pid":"0180660e63fca2743f7e83679dd7f8f4e57a1fb5","tid":51861,"uid":68734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留一線，想收你做兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好令佢日後仲可以利用你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係咁我真係覺得佢好恐怖...<br />\n<br />\n但約好哂、餐廳又佢簡，都可以咁樣放飛機真係唔知佢想點...."},{"pid":"4f5ab181606b1d62b425ee7f5b535ee1fe171a80","tid":51861,"uid":69227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:53:38.000Z","msg":"表白黎做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一表白果刻你已經輸晒"},{"pid":"d23646393ff48f0c8c37e6a8dd038948e1ef6225","tid":51861,"uid":68734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:55:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>表白黎做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一表白果刻你已經輸晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢排都睇左好多巴打分享，我都知衰..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果條女係咁，有時都覺得就算唔講都無咩結果"},{"pid":"7e5db59f0ecb7ebfe6917b72d1489375754dd8ce","tid":51861,"uid":68734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:06:30.000Z","msg":"唉，仲要係聖誕之前<br />\n點解要咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}